BBNaija lockdown housemate, TrikyTee, has been appointed as a Senior Special Assistant to the Bayelsa State Governor, Duoye Diri. TrikyTee disclosed this on his Instagram page on Friday while thanking the Governor for his new appointment. ”I want to thank His Excellency, the Executive Governor of Bayelsa State, Senator Douye Diri on my appointment as a Senior Special Assistant to the Governor of Bayelsa State. “What an Honour, I am grateful,” he wrote. Recall that Nengi who was one of the five top finalists during the Big Brother season 5 show was also given a similar appointment. 